data.Description: Pokémon GO Fest 2023 is coming to Osaka, and we have big plans for one of the largest urban areas in the world! Pokémon GO Fest 2023: Osaka is split into two different experiences between two locations: Expo ’70 Commemorative Park and in Suita City & Osaka City*!

Bonus: Lure Modules activated will last for one hour
Trainers will be able to enjoy Field Research themed around the different Pokémon habitats

Take snapshots during the event—you never know who might show up!
